-- Wise Man Bofinger Sees ‘Very Unfavorable’ Economy, Passauer Says
-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 2012-01-13T04:00:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-13/wise-man-bofinger-sees-very-unfavorable-economy-passauer-says.html
The economic development in the euro
region will be “very unfavorable” this year,  Passauer Neue
Presse  said, citing an interview with  Peter Bofinger , a member
of  Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s council of economic advisers.  Greece  needs further financial help to avoid a
“disorderly” insolvency and a  chain reaction , Bofinger is
cited as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
